title: Imran Khan (Trinidad and Tobago cricketer)
summary: Imran Khan (born 6 July 1984 in Port of Spain) is a West Indian cricketer who plays as a right arm leg spinner. Khan has mainly featured for Trinidad and Tobago in first-class and list-A matches. He has also played for Caribbean Premier League teams Barbados Tridents, Jamaica Tallawahs and the St Kitts and Nevis Patriots.
